              <p>All components are designed to be responsive and look great on all devices.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-6 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Customizable</h3>
              <p>Modify the components to fit your project's style and requirements easily.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

